h]] || [[Caribbean Sea]] || [[Caribbean Plate]] || North American Plate, [[South American Plate]] |- | [[South Sandwich Islands]] || [[United Kingdom]] || [[South Sandwich Trench]] || [[Scotia Sea]] || [[Scotia Plate]] || South American Plate |- | Aegean or [[Hellenic arc]] || [[Greece]] || Eastern Mediterranean Trench || [[Aegean Sea]] || [[Aegean Sea Plate]] or Hellenic Plate || [[African Plate]] |- | [[South Aegean Volcanic Arc]] || Greece || Eastern Mediterranean Trench || Aegean Sea || [[Aegean Sea Plate]] or Hellenic Plate || African Plate |}
